<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="183">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$chen-yi-xuan-21" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/chen-yi-xuan-21" class="zg-link" title="陈逸轩">陈逸轩</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$zheng-william" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/zheng-william" class="zg-link" title="zheng william">zheng william</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$luo-zhong-wei-37" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/luo-zhong-wei-37" class="zg-link" title="小罗威">小罗威</a></span>
